---
title: Prawn Katsu Bao Buns & Cabbage Salad with Spring Onion Fries
description: This week, our favourite fluffy cloud-like buns are packed with crunchy crumbed prawns, a crisp cabbage salad, and a rich katsu sauce. Bao night is quickly becoming a staple in our home, how about yours?
